{"ja505:0.1":"Jataka ","ja505:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja505:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja505:0.4":"9. Somanassajataka ","ja505:1.1":"“Ko tam himsati hetheti, ","ja505:1.2":"Kim dummano socasi appatito; ","ja505:1.3":"Kassajja matapitaro rudantu, ","ja505:1.4":"Kvajja setu nihato pathabya”. ","ja505:2.1":"“Tutthosmi deva tava dassanena, ","ja505:2.2":"Cirassam passami tam bhumipala; ","ja505:2.3":"Ahimsako renumanuppavissa, ","ja505:2.4":"Puttena te hethayitosmi deva”. ","ja505:3.1":"“Ayantu dovarika khaggabandha, ","ja505:3.2":"Kasaviya yantu antepurantam; ","ja505:3.3":"Hantvana tam somanassam kumaram, ","ja505:3.4":"Chetvana sisam varamaharantu”. ","ja505:4.1":"“Pesita rajino duta, ","ja505:4.2":"kumaram etadabravum; ","ja505:4.3":"Issarena vitinnosi, ","ja505:4.4":"vadham pattosi khattiya”. ","ja505:5.1":"“Sa rajaputto paridevayanto, ","ja505:5.2":"Dasangulim anjalim paggahetva; ","ja505:5.3":"Ahampi icchami janinda datthum, ","ja505:5.4":"Jivam mam netva patidassayetha”. ","ja505:6.1":"Tassa tam vacanam sutva, ","ja505:6.2":"ranno puttam adassayum; ","ja505:6.3":"Putto ca pitaram disva, ","ja505:6.4":"duratovajjhabhasatha. ","ja505:7.1":"“Agacchum dovarika khaggabandha, ","ja505:7.2":"Kasaviya hantu mamam janinda; ","ja505:7.3":"Akkhahi me pucchito etamattham, ","ja505:7.4":"Aparadho ko nidha mamajja atthi”. ","ja505:8.1":"“Sayanca pato udakam sajati, ","ja505:8.2":"Aggim sada paricaratappamatto; ","ja505:8.3":"Tam tadisam samyatam brahmacarim, ","ja505:8.4":"Kasma tuvam brusi gahappatiti”. ","ja505:9.1":"“Tala ca mula ca phala ca deva, ","ja505:9.2":"Pariggaha vividha santimassa; ","ja505:9.3":"Te rakkhati gopayatappamatto, ","ja505:9.4":"Tasma aham brumi gahappatiti”. ","ja505:10.1":"“Saccam kho etam vadasi kumara, ","ja505:10.2":"Pariggaha vividha santimassa; ","ja505:10.3":"Te rakkhati gopayatappamatto, ","ja505:10.4":"Sa brahmano gahapati tena hoti”. ","ja505:11.1":"“Sunantu mayham parisa samagata, ","ja505:11.2":"Sanegama janapada ca sabbe; ","ja505:11.3":"Balayam balassa vaco nisamma, ","ja505:11.4":"Ahetuna ghatayate mam janindo. ","ja505:12.1":"Dalhasmi mule visate virulhe, ","ja505:12.2":"Dunnikkayo velu pasakhajato; ","ja505:12.3":"Vandami padani tava janinda, ","ja505:12.4":"Anujana mam pabbajissami deva”. ","ja505:13.1":"“Bhunjassu bhoge vipule kumara, ","ja505:13.2":"Sabbanca te issariyam dadami; ","ja505:13.3":"Ajjeva tvam kurunam hohi raja, ","ja505:13.4":"Ma pabbaji pabbajja hi dukkha”. ","ja505:14.1":"“Kinnudha deva tavamatthi bhoga, ","ja505:14.2":"Pubbevaham devaloke ramissam; ","ja505:14.3":"Rupehi saddehi atho rasehi, ","ja505:14.4":"Gandhehi phassehi manoramehi. ","ja505:15.1":"Bhutta ca me bhoga tidivasmim deva, ","ja505:15.2":"Parivarito accharanam ganena; ","ja505:15.3":"Tuvanca balam paraneyyam viditva, ","ja505:15.4":"Na tadise rajakule vaseyyam”. ","ja505:16.1":"“Sacaham balo paraneyyo asmi, ","ja505:16.2":"Ekaparadham khama putta mayham; ","ja505:16.3":"Punapi ce edisakam bhaveyya, ","ja505:16.4":"Yathamatim somanassa karohi”. ","ja505:17.1":"“Anisamma katam kammam, ","ja505:17.2":"anavatthaya cintitam; ","ja505:17.3":"Bhesajjasseva vebhango, ","ja505:17.4":"vipako hoti papako. ","ja505:18.1":"Nisamma ca katam kammam, ","ja505:18.2":"sammavatthaya cintitam; ","ja505:18.3":"Bhesajjasseva sampatti, ","ja505:18.4":"vipako hoti bhadrako. ","ja505:19.1":"Alaso gihi kamabhogi na sadhu, ","ja505:19.2":"Asannato pabbajito na sadhu; ","ja505:19.3":"Raja na sadhu anisammakari, ","ja505:19.4":"Yo pandito kodhano tam na sadhu. ","ja505:20.1":"Nisamma khattiyo kayira, ","ja505:20.2":"nanisamma disampati; ","ja505:20.3":"Nisammakarino raja, ","ja505:20.4":"yaso kitti ca vaddhati. ","ja505:21.1":"Nisamma dandam panayeyya issaro, ","ja505:21.2":"Vega katam tappati bhumipala; ","ja505:21.3":"Sammapanidhi ca narassa attha, ","ja505:21.4":"Ananutappa te bhavanti paccha. ","ja505:22.1":"Ananutappani hi ye karonti, ","ja505:22.2":"Vibhajja kammayatanani loke; ","ja505:22.3":"Vinnuppasatthani sukhudrayani, ","ja505:22.4":"Bhavanti buddhanumatani tani. ","ja505:23.1":"Agacchum dovarika khaggabandha, ","ja505:23.2":"Kasaviya hantu mamam janinda; ","ja505:23.3":"Matunca ankasmimaham nisinno, ","ja505:23.4":"Akaddhito sahasa tehi deva. ","ja505:24.1":"Katukanhi sambadham sukiccham patto, ","ja505:24.2":"Madhurampi yam jivitam laddha raja; ","ja505:24.3":"Kicchenaham ajja vadha pamutto, ","ja505:24.4":"Pabbajjamevabhimanohamasmi”. ","ja505:25.1":"“Putto tavayam taruno sudhamme, ","ja505:25.2":"Anukampako somanasso kumaro; ","ja505:25.3":"Tam yacamano na labhami svajja, ","ja505:25.4":"Arahasi nam yacitave tuvampi”. ","ja505:26.1":"“Ramassu bhikkhacariyaya putta, ","ja505:26.2":"Nisamma dhammesu paribbajassu; ","ja505:26.3":"Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam, ","ja505:26.4":"Anindito brahmamupehi thanam”. ","ja505:27.1":"“Acchera rupam vata yadisanca, ","ja505:27.2":"Dukkhitam mam dukkhapayase sudhamme; ","ja505:27.3":"Yacassu puttam iti vuccamana, ","ja505:27.4":"Bhiyyova ussahayase kumaram”. ","ja505:28.1":"“Ye vippamutta anavajjabhogino, ","ja505:28.2":"Parinibbuta lokamimam caranti; ","ja505:28.3":"Tamariyamaggam patipajjamanam, ","ja505:28.4":"Na ussahe varayitum kumaram”. ","ja505:29.1":"“Addha have sevitabba sapanna, ","ja505:29.2":"Bahussuta ye bahuthanacintino; ","ja505:29.3":"Yesayam sutvana subhasitani, ","ja505:29.4":"Appossukka vitasoka sudhamma”ti. ","ja505:30.1":"Somanassajatakam navamam. "}